2026-03-28T06:28:29.9606147Z               "distinct": false,
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9606465Z               "id": "1049c6b29d28ee104875cf58ab3f436b1642ffea",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9610257Z               "message": "Fall back to individual sends when batch email delivery fails\n\nWhen SES rejects a multi-recipient send (e.g. one invalid or unverified\naddress), the whole batch silently fails. This change catches the batch\nfailure and retries each address individually, appending a footer note to\nthe email explaining why it was sent individually.\n\n- EmailRenderer.AppendFallbackNote inserts a styled note before the\n  closing HTML tag\n- EmailSchedulerService.SendCustomerEmailAsync catches batch failures,\n  skips fallback for single recipients, sends individually to all\n  To+CC+BCC addresses, re-throws only if every individual send also fails\n- OperationCanceledException propagates immediately without triggering\n  fallback\n- 11 new tests covering all branches: batch success, single-recipient\n  no-fallback, To+CC+BCC combined, cancellation, all-fail rethrow,\n  partial success, and fallback HTML content\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01GYPAPQwDpWkpzVSP1ync2h",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9613984Z               "timestamp": "2026-03-28T01:29:35Z",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9614333Z               "tree_id": "4a360ddc5fa855d99706288ba508e11ece0edc34",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9614890Z               "url": "https://github.com/***/hpoll/commit/1049c6b29d28ee104875cf58ab3f436b1642ffea"
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9615326Z             },
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9615699Z             {
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9615908Z               "author": {
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9616163Z                 "email": "noreply@anthropic.com",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9616452Z                 "name": "Claude",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9616695Z                 "username": "claude"
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9616942Z               },
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9617153Z               "committer": {
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9617414Z                 "email": "noreply@anthropic.com",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9617721Z                 "name": "Claude",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9618125Z                 "username": "claude"
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9618399Z               },
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9618593Z               "distinct": false,
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9618876Z               "id": "4dc0fd3dd6811f5416fb3d7ec88b1e544ef0454b",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9622600Z               "message": "Scope fallback to EmailAddressRejectionException only\n\nReplace broad Exception catch with a custom EmailAddressRejectionException\ntype so transient network errors and cancellations propagate directly\nwithout triggering individual-send fallback.\n\n- EmailAddressRejectionException added to Hpoll.Core.Exceptions\n- SesEmailSender wraps MessageRejectedException as\n  EmailAddressRejectionException; all other exceptions pass through\n- EmailSchedulerService catches only EmailAddressRejectionException for\n  fallback (OperationCanceledException guard no longer needed)\n- SesEmailSenderTests updated: MessageRejectedException wrapped, other\n  exceptions propagate, new network-error test\n- EmailSchedulerServiceTests: fallback tests use\n  EmailAddressRejectionException, new test confirms network errors do\n  not trigger fallback\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01GYPAPQwDpWkpzVSP1ync2h",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9627452Z               "timestamp": "2026-03-28T02:03:15Z",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9627799Z               "tree_id": "cc2c2e03b04911ca5775e0ea797ca2b492d9e693",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9628342Z               "url": "https://github.com/***/hpoll/commit/4dc0fd3dd6811f5416fb3d7ec88b1e544ef0454b"
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9628752Z             },
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9628922Z             {
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9629098Z               "author": {
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9629337Z                 "email": "noreply@anthropic.com",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9629596Z                 "name": "Claude",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9629823Z                 "username": "claude"
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9630047Z               },
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9630221Z               "committer": {
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9630455Z                 "email": "noreply@anthropic.com",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9630720Z                 "name": "Claude",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9630935Z                 "username": "claude"
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9631152Z               },
