2026-03-28T06:28:29.9631595Z               "id": "1adfd49f63f75e523d18e3530be08007849c4bd3",
2026-03-28T06:28:29.9633579Z               "message": "Include CC and BCC in email send log messages\n\nThe success and failure log lines previously only showed To addresses,\nmaking it impossible to confirm whether CC/BCC addresses were actually\npassed to SES. Now all three recipient groups are logged (masked) to\naid diagnosis of delivery issues.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01GYPAPQwDpWkpzVSP1ync2h",
