2026-03-28T06:28:29.9640944Z               "message": "Add tests to improve code coverage for email-related changes\n\n- EmailRenderer: test 5+ active areas diversity label, null nowUtc fallback\n- SesEmailSender: test CC/BCC in MessageRejected and generic error paths\n- EmailSchedulerService: test ExecuteAsync unhandled exception retry path\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01BqSLpo68yWsmYXBwT8J34y",
